text:
Oh, Asahi. You're eager.
Let's discuss it when we get back home...

I feel like I gained a lot from the training camp!
I want to try them out soon~

Is that so...!
That makes the training camp worthwhile.

Yes!
I want to come again!

Yeah,
because we haven't finished exploring everything yet.

Yeah, you know~
We found rivers and waterfalls, but...
If we keep looking, we might find caves or hideouts.

There's still time, right?
Can we go check them out?

I see, maybe it's because you're enjoying
the training camp and exploring so much.

Alright, I need to work hard
so that Asahi can enjoy herself.

Got it, got it.
Let's go together...!
